Commands ----------------------------------------------------------------

check npm 
check node 
npm install -g typescript
check tsc version 
npm install -g ts-node (run typescript file directly)

 1) npm init --y
 2) tsc --init
 3) npm install @types/node


Run
 1)tsc (it will convert the ts file to js) ---> node js_file_name
 Or
 1)ts-node file_name.ts

Express:: 
 "npm i express @types/express nodemon ts-node @types/node typescript"
 
 Run 
  1-package.json { start : "nodemon ./src/index.ts" }
  2-npm start
  (restart your system if not working)

